{
  "page": "Mord",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Mord</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mord by Paolo Puggioni.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg/350px-Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg/525px-Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/52/Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg/700px-Mord_by_Paolo_Puggioni.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Mord, by Paolo Puggioni © Green Ronin Publishing</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nCiaran Bermingham</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_1\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mord</b> is a gaoler of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>, who is in charge of the upkeep and maintenance of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sky_cells\" title=\"Sky cells\">sky cells</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Mord is portrayed by Ciaran Bermingham.<sup id=\"cite_ref-IMDB_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-IMDB-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Mord\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Mord</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Mord\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Mord</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Mord\" title=\"Category:Images of Mord\">Images of Mord</a></div>\n<p>Mord is a large man, who weighs twenty stone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> He has rotting brown teeth, and small dark eyes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The left side of his face is scarred and lopsided from an axe which cut off an ear and part of his cheek.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Mord has a heavy white belly, and thick fingers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>A brutish man, Mord is fond of tormenting his prisoners, telling them they are going to fall out of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sky_cells\" title=\"Sky cells\">sky cells</a> to their deaths.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> considers Mord to be an oaf who is often tricked.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Mord's clothes fit poorly and have a rank, ripe smell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> He wears steel-toed boots and threatens prisoners with a leather strap<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and a lash.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mord_JM.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Mord_JM.png/350px-Mord_JM.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"226\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Mord_JM.png/525px-Mord_JM.png 1.5x, /images/5/5a/Mord_JM.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mord_JM.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Mord by Jake Murray © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> is brought up to the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a>, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> orders Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a> to have the <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">dwarf</a> thrown into the <a href=\"/index.php/Sky_cells\" title=\"Sky cells\">sky cells</a>. Mord claims Tyrion's magnificent <a href=\"/index.php/Shadowskin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shadowskin\">shadowskin</a> cloak. The gaoler repeatedly taunts Tyrion, dropping the prisoner's food over the side on one occasion. Mord beats Tyrion with his leather strap, but Tyrion bribes the turnkey with the promise of <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> if Mord tells Lysa that Tyrion wishes to confess his crimes. Mord reluctantly returns the cloak to Tyrion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Within the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Hall\" title=\"High Hall\">High Hall</a>, Tyrion publicly demands <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and his champion, <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a>, ends up slaying Lysa's representative, Ser Vardis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Before leaving the Eyrie, Tyrion pays Mord his purse of gold, and offers another reward if he ever comes to <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Mord has capped his teeth with gold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> has Mord <a href=\"/index.php/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">torture</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a>, a prisoner in the sky cells. <a href=\"/index.php/Fat_Maddy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fat Maddy\">Fat Maddy</a> states that Mord has removed both pinkies and a ring finger from the singer's hands. Marillion falsely confesses to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Nestor_Royce\" title=\"Nestor Royce\">Nestor Royce</a> that he killed Lysa.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the Arryn court descends to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a> before the onset of winter, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a> helps Mord load supplies into buckets in the winch room. Mord is one of the last to leave the Eyrie, as he is tasked with butchering the oxen in the winch room before he leaves.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Mord\">Quotes by Mord</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Mord\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg/350px-Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg/525px-Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c0/Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg/700px-Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tyrion_and_Mord.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Peter Dinklage as <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>, and Ciaran Bermingham as Mord, in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Mord</b>: Is lie. <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">Dwarf</a> man cheat me.<br />\n</p><p><b>Tyrion</b>: I will put my promise in writing.<br />\n<b>Mord</b>: Writing down <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a>. Much gold.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Tyrion</b>: Oh, much gold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Mord and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Mord\">Quotes about Mord</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Mord\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The turnkey was twenty stone of gross stupidity, with brown rotting teeth and small dark eyes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mord may be a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to Mord, a fictitious executioner played by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boris_Karloff\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Boris Karloff\">Boris Karloff</a> in the movie <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tower_of_London_(1939_film)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tower of London (1939 film)\">Tower of London</a></i>. The movie is about the life of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_III_of_England\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Richard III of England\">Richard III of England</a>, a known source of inspiration for Martin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafmord.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Mord.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-IMDB-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-IMDB_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0944947/epcast\">Cast of Game of Thrones on IMDB</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">3.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\">3.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\">3.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\">3.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-7\">3.7</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-8\">3.8</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-9\">3.9</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">4.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\">4.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Sansa I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"